th="1480" height="44" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n_7e1e5d80da" parent="1" value="🟪 &lt;b&gt;API Call #3&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&apos;#991b1b&apos;&gt;&lt;b&gt;messages length = 5&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Claude sees:&lt;br&gt;• original query&lt;br&gt;• search result IDs&lt;br&gt;• all 5 extracted paper details" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;spacing=4;spacingTop=4;spacingRight=4;spacingBottom=4;spacingLeft=4;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Helvetica;fillColor=#f3e8ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontColor=#111827;fontSize=15;" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="1795" width="360" height="190" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n_c4ea2ef51b" parent="1" value="🤖 &lt;b&gt;Claude response.content&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Content blocks:&lt;/b&gt; 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.&lt;/b&gt; text only&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&apos;#991b1b&apos;&gt;&lt;b&gt;No tool_use blocks&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;spacing=4;spacingTop=4;spacingRight=4;spacingBottom=4;spacingLeft=4;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Helvetica;fillColor=#f3e8ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontColor=#111827;fontSize=15;" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="465" y="1795" width="315" height="170" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n_f69bbdc74b" parent="1" value="✅ &lt;b&gt;Final Answer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Claude summarizes the 5 papers:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1.&lt;/b&gt; title&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;2.&lt;/b&gt; authors&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;3.&lt;/b&gt; published date&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;4.&lt;/b&gt; summary&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;5.&lt;/b&gt; PDF link" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;spacing=4;spacingTop=4;spacingRight=4;spacingBottom=4;spacingLeft=4;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Helvetica;fillColor=#f3e8ff;strokeColor=#9333ea;fontColor=#111827;fontSize=15;" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="845" y="1795" width="335" height="205" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n_420bda5e6b" parent="1" value="◇&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;tool_results&lt;br&gt;empty?&lt;/b&gt;" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;spacing=4;spacingTop=4;spacingRight=4;spacingBottom=4;spacingLeft=4;fillColor=#ffedd5;strokeColor=#f97316;fontColor=#111827;fontSize=15;fontStyle=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontFamily=Helvetica;" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="1245" y="1820" width="155" height="125" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n_41df9c0405" parent="1" value="🏁 &lt;b&gt;End Loop&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;code&gt;break&lt;/code&gt;" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;rounded=0;spacing=4;spacingTop=4;spacingRight=4;spacingBottom=4;spacingLeft=4;fillColor=#dcfce7;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontColor=#111827;fontSize=17;fontStyle=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontFamily=Helvetica;" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="1430" y="1835" width="90" height="95" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="e_3aa89d04c2" parent="1" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;endArrow=block;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#475569;fontSize=12;fontColor=#334155;" edge="1" source="n_10acb17ebb" target="n_7e1e5d80da"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="1230" y="1680"/><mxPoint x="220" y="1680"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e_184e7699f0" parent="1" style="edgeStyle=none;rounded=0;html=1;endArrow=block;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#475569;fontSize=12;fontColor=#334155;" edge="1" source="n_7e1e5d80da" target="n_c4ea2ef51b"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e_83a894ca93" parent="1" style="edgeStyle=none;rounded=0;html=1;endArrow=block;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#475569;fontSize=12;fontColor=#334155;" edge="1" source="n_c4ea2ef51b" target="n_f69bbdc74b"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e_a8095ee9f3" parent="1" style="edgeStyle=none;rounded=0;html=1;endArrow=block;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#475569;fontSize=12;fontColor=#334155;" edge="1" source="n_f69bbdc74b" target="n_420bda5e6b"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e_64e4ebab35" parent="1" value="Yes" style="edgeStyle=none;rounded=0;html=1;endArrow=block;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#475569;fontSize=12;fontColor=#334155;" edge="1" source="n_420bda5e6b" target="n_41df9c0405"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="n_3cab9ae732" parent="1" value="
✅ &lt;b&gt;Important conclusions from this run&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;table border=&apos;0&apos; cellpadding=&apos;3&apos; cellspacing=&apos;0&apos;&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign=&apos;top&apos;&gt;🔎&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;b&gt;Round 1&lt;/b&gt; contained only &lt;font color=&apos;#047857&apos;&gt;&lt;b&gt;one tool_use&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;: &lt;code&gt;search_papers&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign=&apos;top&apos;&gt;📦&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;b&gt;Round 2&lt;/b&gt; contained &lt;font color=&apos;#7c3aed&apos;&gt;&lt;b&gt;six content blocks&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;: one text block + five &lt;code&gt;extract_info&lt;/code&gt; tool_use blocks.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign=&apos;top&apos;&gt;⏱️&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;extract_info&lt;/code&gt; was &lt;b&gt;not&lt;/b&gt; called before &lt;code&gt;search_papers&lt;/code&gt; returned real paper IDs.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign=&apos;top&apos;&gt;➡️&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;The five &lt;code&gt;extract_info&lt;/code&gt; calls were executed &lt;font color=&apos;#047857&apos;&gt;&lt;b&gt;sequentially&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; by Python, not in parallel.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign=&apos;top&apos;&gt;🔗&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;All &lt;code&gt;tool_result&lt;/code&gt; blocks from the same Claude response must be returned &lt;font color=&apos;#991b1b&apos;&gt;&lt;b&gt;together&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td valign=&apos;top&apos;&gt;🧠&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;response.content&lt;/code&gt; is one Claude output; &lt;code&gt;messages&lt;/code&gt; is the full accumulated conversation state.&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
